  <brief_title>Early Continuous Renal Replacement Therapies (CRRT) in Patients With Severe Sepsis or Septic Shock With Acute Kidney Injury</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Multi-Center Trial of the Early Application of CRRT in Patients With Severe Sepsis or Septic Shock</official_title>
